3xp7 | Check out Rick Hanson's Hardwiring Happiness or Joe Dispenza's Becoming Supernatural, which both focus on how to create positive changes within your inner landscape.
2hce | Start to identify the parts of you that do function in secure ways and focus on how to make them more prominent in your life. What daily practices or perspectives can you take on that bring your preferred expression of self more to the front and center in your life?
12p5 | Let yourself laugh and seek out humor.
